The paper focuses on a human-in-the-loop machine learning system for text analytics, which involves natural language processing and deep learning techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the role of humans in the machine learning process, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The interaction between humans and machines is a key aspect of the paper, which suggests cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as another likely sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with text analytics and information retrieval, which could be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
